{
  "id": "adv_bond_ktn_01_04",
  "title": "長瀬琴乃4",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_04-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……どうしてもっていうから引き受けちゃったけど\nなんで私達が、すずの部屋を片付けるの……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haa… I said I would do it because she asked me to‚\nbut why do we have to clean Suzu-chan's room…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 7.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 11.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_04-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "「今日の夕方までに片付けなかったら、全部捨てます」\nって沙季ちゃんと約束してたみたい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "'If I don't clean up by this evening‚ I'll throw it all away'\nShe'd promised Saki-chan",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 18.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_04-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "その当日に、本人はお仕事が入っちゃってた訳だけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But‚ she had work that day",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 23.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_04-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "それなら前もって、片付けておけばいいのに……\n面倒なことを押し付けられた気がする",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then‚ it would be better to clean up in advance…\nI feel like I've taken on a troublesome task",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 31.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_04-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "そう言いながら引き受けちゃうあたり\n琴乃ちゃんらしいよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even though you say that‚ you end up taking on the work\nThat's so Kotono-chan",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 35.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_04-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "だって、すずがあんなに頼むから……\nそれより、早く片付けましょう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I mean‚ Suzu-chan asked me to do it so much…\nRather than that‚ let's clean up quickly‚ okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 40.5
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 43.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_04-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、そうだね\nじゃあ琴乃ちゃんは、ベッドの周りをお願いね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufu‚ yeah\nThen‚ Kotono-chan‚ please clean up around the bed",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.7,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 21066.666666700003
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 50.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_04-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "もぉ、なんでゲームソフトがベッドの上にあるのよ……\n棚に戻して、っと。……？　何かしら、この紙……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Seriously why are those game titles on the bed…\nPut them back‚ on the shelf‚ …? What is‚ this paper…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 62.9
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 67.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_04-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "何か書いてあるね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There's something written on it",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 69.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_04-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "えっと……『ひまですわ。ああひまですわ。ひまですわ\nひまひまひま宮、すず様ですわ。あぁひま』……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um… \"I’m bored‚ Ahhh‚ so bored‚ I’m bored‚\nI am Bored-bored-bored-miya‚ Suzu‚ Ahhh‚ I’m so\"…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 83.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_04-ngs006.m4a",
      "text": "落書きみたいだね……\nこんなこと書くなんて、よっぽど暇だったのかな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It looks like scribble…\nShe must have been really bored to write something like this",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 90.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_04-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "そんなに暇なら自分で片付けてほしかったんだけど……\nあと、なんで五・七・五・八・七・四……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If she was that bored‚ I wish she would clean up after herself…\nAlso‚ what is it 5-7-5-8-7-4…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 100.4795575701
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_04-ngs007.m4a",
      "text": "すずちゃんの部屋って、不思議なものが落ちてるね\nこの鎧とか、置いてあるものも不思議だけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There are strange things lying around in Suzu-chan's room\nThis armor and other things are strange‚ too",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.4795575701,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 109.6333277385
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_04-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "そうね。あそこの変な石も、なんの意味が……\nいっそ、一回全部片付けた方がいい気がするけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ What's the meaning of that weird stone over there‚ too…\nI think it would be better for her to sort everything out once",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.6333277385,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 10966.6712442
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 115.5999989827
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 120.2666610718
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_04-ktn008.m4a",
      "text": "あ……この雑誌、お姉ちゃんが表紙だ……\n『バレンタインCMで話題沸騰中』……可愛い衣装……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah… this magazine‚ my sister is on the cover…\n\"Currently a hot topic in the Valentine's Day CM\"… Cute outfit…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.2666610718,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 132.6999944051
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_04-ngs008.m4a",
      "text": "ほんとだ、可愛いね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're right‚ it's so cute",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.6999944051,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 135.9999944051
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_04-ktn009.m4a",
      "text": "あ……東京レイーズの時のタオル……\nかっこいい系のデザインなんだ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah… the towel from Tokyo Rays…\nIt's a cool design…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.9999944051,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_04-ktn010.m4a",
      "text": "パンフレットもある……\nわ、この写真初めて見た……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There's also a pamphlet…\nWow‚ this is my first time seeing this photo…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.2999944051,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 149.4333277385
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_04-ngs009.m4a",
      "text": "さすが、すずちゃんだね\nでも琴乃ちゃん、急がないと夕方までに終わらないよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Indeed‚ Suzu-chan\nBut Kotono-chan‚ if you don't hurry‚ you won't be done by this evening?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.4333277385,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 156.3333389283
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_04-ktn011.m4a",
      "text": "あ……だ、大丈夫！　なんだかやる気出てきたから\n捨てちゃうのがもったいないものも、あるみたいだし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah… i-it's okay! I'm feeling motivated now\nIt seems like there are some things that too good to throw away",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 156.3333389283,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 166.800005595
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
